HEADWORD: Soda fountain
<hw>So"da foun`tain</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a counter at
which people may sit and be served soda pop, ice cream, or light meals.
Such counters may be located for example in restaurants, ice cream
shops, drugstores, departments stores.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

